00:15:38.740 --> 00:15:41.200
to the world of comic
books I left that world

00:15:41.200 --> 00:15:44.090
in a shadow here, brought
me back, thank you.

00:15:44.090 --> 00:15:47.730
And Jacqueline Woodson, what
a gift to the world you are,

00:15:47.730 --> 00:15:51.180
you teach us, you guide us, you
make us wiser, better, stronger,

00:15:51.180 --> 00:15:55.010
this last [inaudible] work the
summer was just the coolest

00:15:55.010 --> 00:15:59.500
phone call ever, it was just all
about the love of books and art

00:15:59.500 --> 00:16:01.630
and illustration
and the highlight

00:16:01.630 --> 00:16:04.560
of the last year was your
selection as the ambassador.

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:07.650
We're happy for you, your
family, for us and mostly,

00:16:07.650 --> 00:16:09.580
for the young people you'll
reach with your message

00:16:09.580 --> 00:16:11.700
and energy and the
power of storytelling.

00:16:11.700 --> 00:16:14.620
Thank you all of you and the
children of the book world,

00:16:14.620 --> 00:16:16.080
you make a difference every day.

00:16:16.080 --> 00:16:17.380
We'll see again soon

