&gt;&gt; The Olympics [laughter]

00:24:36.180 --> 00:24:37.820
&gt;&gt; Awesome.

00:24:37.820 --> 00:24:40.160
[Applauding]

00:24:40.160 --> 00:24:41.460
Get a three some.

00:24:41.460 --> 00:24:43.160
[Applauding]

