So I'm not going to
be long because I am

00:40:03.020 --> 00:40:06.480
so much more interested in your
questions maybe I'll answer a

00:40:06.480 --> 00:40:08.910
few of them and what
I have to say,

00:40:08.910 --> 00:40:13.120
but I love when young
people ask me questions.

00:40:13.120 --> 00:40:16.770
But I was told I
needed to say something

00:40:16.770 --> 00:40:18.490
about becoming ambassador.

