Every Child a reader and
the committee that chose me

00:43:38.440 --> 00:43:44.410
to succeed, Gene, DeAndra,
Sarah, Earl, Travis,

00:43:44.410 --> 00:43:50.500
Starr and Ellen and of course,
Gene, I love your faith in me

00:43:50.500 --> 00:43:58.440
and I'm grateful, I
think [laughter] for it.

00:43:58.440 --> 00:44:03.290
I wouldn't be standing here
without my Penguin family,

00:44:03.290 --> 00:44:08.520
my long suffering editor Nancy
Paulsen [laughter] Jen, Ellis,

00:44:08.520 --> 00:44:13.900
Jocelyn, Felicia, Cecilia
