before it became the book
so many of y' all have read

00:44:29.750 --> 00:44:33.770
and some tweaks between the
first and second addition,

00:44:33.770 --> 00:44:36.060
so if you have that
first addition,

00:44:36.060 --> 00:44:41.620
hold on [laughter] my eyes
in the world are my own world

00:44:41.620 --> 00:44:44.870
and the eyes of those who
I trust deeply, Nancy,

00:44:44.870 --> 00:44:48.120
thank you for being my second
set of eyes in the world.

